(b) math.sin(2 * math.pi) --> -2.4492935982947064e-16
(k) round(3.5) --> 4
(c) math.cos(2 * math.pi) --> 1.0
(l) round(-2.5) --> -2
(d) min(2, 2, 1) --> 1
(m) math.fabs(2.5) --> 2.5
(e) math.log(math.e) --> 1.0
(n) math.ceil(2.5) -->3
(f) math.exp(1) --> 2.718281828459045
(o) math.floor(2.5) --> 2
(g) max(2, 3, 4) --> 4
(p) round(-2.5) --> -2
(h) abs(-2.5) --> 2.5
(q) round(2.6) --> 3
(i) math.ceil(-2.5) --> -2
(r) round(math.fabs(-2.5)) --> 2

